Common.Strapline.Common.Text: EFFICIENT, FUNCTIONAL & FULLY RACKED - HIGH CLEARANCE WAREHOUSE WITH EXCELLENT ACCESS

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to exclusively offer, For Lease, Assembly, located at 1727-1787 Hume Highway, Campbellfield.

Formerly the home of Ford Australia, Assembly will provide Melbourne’s North with an industrial business park capable of accommodating prospective tenants with areas from 2,500 –118,000sqm*.
 
The strategically located site is situated on the corner of the Hume Highway and Barry Road, providing exceptional access to major road arterials such as the Metropolitan Ring Road, Tullamarine Freeway, Cooper Street and the Calder Freeway. Further, the property benefits from extensive frontage to the Hume Highway.

The business park will cater to manufacturing, warehousing and logistics tenants, as well as interfacing future retail, office, childcare and hotel uses.

Key property attributes include:
+ Building areas available from 2,500-118,000sqm*
+ Huge power supply and gas availability
+ Expansive hardstand areas
+ Ideal for manufacturing and logistics uses
+ Opportunity to cater for future growth
+ Future integrated business park
+ Secure  your position early and customise your tenancy to suit your businesses requirements

For further information regarding this property or to arrange an inspection of the site, kindly contact CBRE.

*approx.
